title: 33(23) The regulations for Transit Oriented Development (TOD) FSI with the other conditionality to promote densification along Mass Transport Corridor will be formulated separately
clause_text: 33(23) The regulations for Transit Oriented Development (TOD) FSI with the other conditionality to promote densification along Mass Transport Corridor will be formulated separately. The Proposed Land-use plan depicts the land use zones.
